OL,3,CBritish workers among most reluctant
OL,4,Cin the world to return to office
OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FFive years on from the first
OL,8,Fcoronavirus lockdown, workers in the
OL,9,FUK are tied with Spain as the second
OL,10,Fmost reluctant to go into the office,
OL,11,Fa new poll suggests.
OL,13,FBrits were beaten only by workers in
OL,14,Fthe Philippines, according to a survey
OL,15,Fby property agents JLL, which shows
OL,16,Fthere remains a "significant" gap in
OL,17,Fthe return to office expectations of
OL,18,Femployers and their staff.
