OL,3,CBritish workers among most reluctant
OL,4,Cin the world to return to office
OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FAcross the board, workers in the UK
OL,8,Fare spending just two days a week on
OL,9,Faverage in the office. That is about
OL,10,Fhalf as many days as before the
OL,11,Fpandemic, but is still more than most
OL,12,FBrits would like.
OL,14,FOn average UK workers want to be going
OL,15,Finto the office about 1.5 days per
OL,16,Fweek, according to the survey of
OL,17,F12,000 workers in 44 countries.
