OL,7,FMeanwhile, Filipino workers are going
OL,8,Fin 1.4 days per week, on average,
OL,9,Falthough most would rather do less
OL,10,Fthan a full day's work in the office.
OL,12,FKuwait is leading the way in the post-
OL,13,Fpandemic return to the office, with
OL,14,Fstaff working from their company's
OL,15,Foffices for 4.2 days a week, more than
OL,16,Fthe 3.5 days they would like to be
OL,17,Fdoing
