OL,4,Cin the world to return to office
OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FGreece is the only country where
OL,8,Fcompanies and their staff get the
OL,9,Fbalance the same: workers want to be
OL,10,Fin the office about 3.5 days per week,
OL,11,Fwhich is roughly what they are doing.
OL,13,FThe findings also highlight age-
OL,14,Frelated differences in office
OL,15,Fexperiences. While the oldest group
OL,16,F(55+) adapted best overall, they are
OL,17,Fmore sensitive to physical conditions
OL,18,Flike temperature, noise, and air
OL,19,Fquality, particularly its impact on
OL,20,Ffocused work.
