OL,7,FYounger workers (up to 24 years old)
OL,8,Fare in the office on average 3 days a
OL,9,Fweek, tracking higher than all other
OL,10,Fage groups.
OL,12,FThe middle group (35-54) report the
OL,13,Flowest satisfaction, citing similar
OL,14,Fenvironmental concerns, along with
OL,15,Fdesires for improved technology,
OL,16,Fflexibility, and food options.
