OL,7,FHowever, despite being in the office
OL,8,Fthe most, younger employees (up to 34)
OL,9,Freported the lowest workplace
OL,10,Fwellbeing, ranking it as one of the
OL,11,Flowest performing factors; this group
OL,12,Fprioritised work-life balance,
OL,13,Fflexibility, and healthy food options
OL,14,Fdemonstrating the higher expectations
OL,15,Fthey have of their employers when it
OL,16,Fcomes to wellbeing.
