OL,4,Cin the world to return to office
OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,F"Over the past few years we had
OL,8,Fachieved a reasonable equilibrium in
OL,9,Fthe workplace ` a balance between
OL,10,Femployer expectations and employee
OL,11,Fflexibility," Sue Asprey Price, JLL's
OL,12,FEuropean head of work dynamics, said.
OL,14,F"However, the recent emphasis on
OL,15,Fstricter return-to-office policies
OL,16,Fmeans this balance is now being re-
OL,17,Fexamined by many employers."
OL,19,FAsprey Price said the findings show
OL,20,Fthat a "significant generational
OL,21,Fdivide has emerged".
