OL,5,Cworking
OL,7,FShe added: "Lockdowns shaped a whole
OL,8,Fgeneration of younger workers who
OL,9,Fspent their later education and early
OL,10,Fworking lives without the cultural,
OL,11,Fsocial and professional benefits that
OL,12,Fbeing with other people can bring.
OL,14,F"We're now seeing a big reaction from
OL,15,Fthat generation, with being in the
OL,16,Foffice key to their experience of
OL,17,Fhappy and fulfilling work."
